This paper is about cross-lingual document classification, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of embeddings and deep learning models, which are common in sub-categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DL (Deep Learning).
